https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=50029	45158
匿名读者&nbsp; 写道 <i>"CNN主持人Chris Cuomo在其节目中<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7DcATG9Qy_A" target="_blank" title="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7DcATG9Qy_A">称</a>（YouTube）查看WikiLeaks泄露的有关希拉里的邮件是<a href="http://dailycaller.com/2016/10/16/cnn-host-claims-its-illegal-for-public-to-view-wikileaks-emails-video/" target="_blank" title="http://dailycaller.com/2016/10/16/cnn-host-claims-its-illegal-for-public-to-view-wikileaks-emails-video/">非法</a>的，但媒体不同，所以美国人民应该通过像CNN这样的媒体了解其邮件内容。"</i>